collections.name: Alpha Gramps
collections.description:
Back in the day, old men started their mornings at the market.
Alpha Gramps? They kick off the day with heavy deadlifts!
Chessboards have been swapped for dumbbells, and Sunday walks replaced with intense gym sessions.
Beer bottles? Now it's all about protein shakes and creatine shots.
Canes? Nah, they’re curling 50kg dumbbells instead.

These OG legends don’t waste time gossiping on park benches—they’re flexing at the squat rack. No more knitted sweaters, just leather jackets, gold chains, and designer fits that command respect. Their music? Bass-heavy beats that shake the room, not old radio classics.

Alpha Gramps aren’t just old men—they’re timeless powerhouses who refuse to slow down. In a world that’s always changing, they chose to dominate.

💪 Strength. Style. Legacy. Welcome to the league of those who never age, only evolve! 🚀🔥
